org.simpleyaml.configuration.comments.format

Interface CommentFormatter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BlankLineYamlCommentFormatter, PrettyYamlCommentFormatter, YamlCommentFormatter, YamlHeaderFormatter

    public interface CommentFormatter
    Converts a comment between a raw-format meant to be read by computers to a human-format meant to be read by humans and vice versa.
